  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK237">
<l>pukaḻpaṭa vāḻātār tannōvār tammai</l>
<l>yikaḻvārai nōva tevaṉ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Why do those who cannot live with praise, grieve those who despise them, instead of grieving themselves for their own inability.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
